  <section class="mb-10">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Enterprise LMS Pricing</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Enterprise platforms operate in a different pricing universe. Instead of published plan pages, they use sales-negotiated contracts based on user count, features, support level, and deployment complexity.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Docebo</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Custom pricing starting around <strong>$10,000-25,000/year</strong> depending on configuration. Per-user pricing models typically range from $4-8 per active user per month. Includes deep Salesforce integration, LTI support, SCIM provisioning, and 400+ native connectors. Best for companies with 500+ learners and complex integration requirements.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Absorb LMS</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Custom pricing, typically <strong>$800+/month</strong> with per-user pricing models. Known for clean UI and strong mobile support. Includes SCORM/xAPI, LTI 1.3, Salesforce integration, and branded mobile apps. Best for mid-market companies that want enterprise features without enterprise complexity.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">TalentLMS</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      The most transparent enterprise pricing: <strong>$69/month (Core)</strong> for up to 40 users, scaling to $459/month (Premium) for up to 1,000 users. Unlimited users available on Enterprise. The most accessible entry point for companies needing LTI, SCORM, SSO, and corporate training features without five-figure annual commitments.
    </p>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-navy mb-3">Thinkific Plus</h3>
    <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
      Custom pricing that bridges expert-focused and enterprise markets. Adds unlimited students, SCORM support, SSO/SAML, branded mobile app, and dedicated support. Ideal for training businesses and academies that need enterprise authentication and compliance features alongside Thinkific's course-selling capabilities.
    </p>
  </section>

